query.query: SELECT id AS id, created_at AS timestamp, customer_id AS customer_id, toDecimal(amount_captured, 10) AS original_amount, upper(currency) AS original_currency, in(original_currency, ['BIF', 'CLP', 'DJF', 'GNF', 'JPY', 'KMF', 'KRW', 'MGA', 'PYG', 'RWF', 'UGX', 'VND', 'VUV', 'XAF', 'XOF', 'XPF']) AS currency_is_zero_decimal, if(currency_is_zero_decimal, toDecimal(1, 10), toDecimal(100, 10)) AS amount_decimal_divider, divideDecimal(original_amount, amount_decimal_divider) AS adjusted_original_amount, 'USD' AS currency, convertCurrency(original_currency, currency, adjusted_original_amount, _toDate(ifNull(timestamp, toDateTime(0)))) AS amount FROM production_stripe_charge WHERE equals(status, 'succeeded')
SELECT id AS id, created_at AS timestamp, name AS name, email AS email, phone AS phone FROM production_stripe_customer
